exthheader.author: Helen Reilly
exthheader.description: Mrs. Reilly again demonstrates her uncanny talent for putting together the pieces of a complex plot in a most plausible manner. The richness of her setting and the believability of her many characters help to sustain the reader's interest to the very end of this ingenious story.
